### 4. 상품 1 재고 증가
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/products/{{productId1}}/inventory/increase
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 50
}

###

